  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Brimonidine Tartrate Ophthalmic Solution in Adult and Geriatric Subjects With Ocular Redness.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of Brimonidine Tartrate Ophthalmic Solution 0.025% Used Four Times Daily in a Population of Adult and Geriatric Subjects With Ocular Redness</official_title>
