  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare the efficacy and safety of brimonidine tartrate ophthalmic solution 0.025% with
      its vehicle for treating ocular redness in a population of adult and geriatric participants
      with ocular redness.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
